ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes. It is a comprehensive discussion of the issues pertaining to the recent financial crisis including regulation.

If a fellow student is interested in banking crises then she should definitely take this course. Also for somebody that isn't yet it might be a valuable course to take since the topics covered are broad and the lectures where overall insightful for me.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Gave me a good sense of financial crises from the experts on the topic

It extremely broadened my knowledge about the recent and also past financial crises. It helped me to realize what we as a profession can say with some certainty and what we still do not know. Since it has touched on many open questions it has provided me with possible areas of research.
